children.subject: I hope everything is well with your family!

history.content:
Hi all,

I had moved my office hours to Friday this weekend because I was going to be visiting family (in Houston) but mother nature has informed me this probably wouldn't be the best weekend for that.

Office hours will still be tonight (Friday, 9PM EST). The slido event code is #CS8803-Sat. You can view the office hours here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fo64_gkpLcc

Since my weekend plans have changed I will also be available tomorrow via email and will be closely watching Piazza as well.

Best (and happy Labor Day),

Michael
